02:03:16.220 --> 02:03:17.842
LAURA: I thought you took the book.

02:03:17.842 --> 02:03:20.120
LIAM: I don't carry books.

02:03:20.120 --> 02:03:22.077
LAURA: No, you have the book. I thought you were
