02:03:22.077 --> 02:03:25.205
You actually have the book, right?

02:03:25.205 --> 02:03:27.091
LIAM: You took the book when we left--

02:03:27.091 --> 02:03:29.516
LAURA: I didn't take the book, I thought you took
