03:00:06.820 --> 03:00:14.120
beating heart of the Raven Queen's worship. As you
approach the front stairway, both of you familiar

03:00:14.120 --> 03:00:24.540
with, one brought in, the other not met with any
living person for the most part in your journey,

03:00:24.598 --> 03:00:28.547
you both approach-- still arms hooked?

03:00:28.547 --> 03:00:29.513
LIAM: No.

03:00:29.513 --> 03:00:31.008
MATT: Okay.

03:00:31.008 --> 03:00:33.571
LIAM: I suspect you've been here before.

03:00:33.571 --> 03:00:35.296
TALIESIN: Yes.

03:00:43.816 --> 03:00:54.274
LIAM: (sighs) I like that things are better
between you and I now.

03:00:54.345 --> 03:01:02.189
TALIESIN: I feel the same. I like that most things
are better now. Not everything, but it's a

03:01:02.189 --> 03:01:05.178
